17. Troubleshooting
- If the backend is not running, the frontend may show an API error.
- If port 3002 is busy, stop the conflicting process or change the backend port.
- If SQLite cannot build on Windows, use the JSON fallback mode.
- If product images do not show, confirm the backend is serving /uploads correctly.
- If admin routes do not load, confirm the admin account exists and the session is active.

